snippet.textDisplay:
[Intro: Vandana & Suman Devi]
Jhod ke kinaare baithi
Sochi jaaun bebe ri main
Uski gali na jaandi theek tha
Issa laga rog mere
Raata ne yo aage ghere
Dil rehve ronda aur cheekhda

[Pre-Chorus: Dhanda Nyoliwala and Xvir Grewal]
Bachi hoi kat ja taawli
Fikra ne kardi saawli
Nyu to sambhal ke chaali thi
Ishq ne kardi bawli
Bawli bawli kardi re
Bawli bawli kardi re

[Sargam: Xvir Grewal and Dhanda Nyoliwala]
Ni sa ni sa re ma re ma
Re sa sa re sa sa sa ni
Ni sa ni sa re ma re ma
Re sa sa re sa sa sa ni
Ni sa ni sa re ma re ma
Re sa sa re sa sa sa ni
Pa ga ma re re sa

[Chorus: Dhanda Nyoliwala]
Logo re ishq na kariyo
Be aayi maut na mariyo
Sutya ke teer tootenge
Mirze jyu pyaar na kariyo

[Refrain: Xvir Grewal]
Pyaar na kariyo na kariyo

[Verse 1: Dhanda Nyoliwala]
Kise ka saath diya, kise te kara kinaara
Kise ne milu roz, kade na jaaun dobara
Bade roye hai mere gale lag-lag ke
Bada ne peeth mein hai khanjar maara
I feel alone
Tere bina mera jeena jyu sailaab ke baad
Bachi Ganga ke kinaare dhauli raakh ke baad
Aankh khuli jaise sunahre khwaab ke baad
Jaise ghar mein jawaan beti baap ke baad

[Verse 2: Dhanda Nyoliwala]
Re jisne jitni zarurat thi loga ne main baant liya
Tere jaane ke baad dekh main dukha ne chaat liya
Ibb meri manzil nahi, umr bhar ka hoon musaafir
Pyaar te aitbaar utha, ishq karu banu kaafir

[Verse 3: Dhanda Nyoliwala]
Rang bhi ud liya ib teri tasveer mein te
Rooh bhi ud li jisam ke zanjeer mein te
Haath dekh jhooth boli tere us fakeer ne re
Wo to kehve tha tu nahi jaani taqdeer mein te

[Refrain: Dhanda Nyoliwala]
Jaani taqdeer mein te
Jaani taqdeer mein te

[Chorus: Dhanda Nyoliwala]
Logo re ishq na kariyo
Be aayi maut na mariyo
Sutya ke teer tootenge
Mirze jyu pyaar na kariyo

[Refrain: Xvir Grewal]
Pyaar na kariyo na kariyo

[Instrumental Break]

[Verse 4: Xvir Grewal]
Re ek ghar banaya hai manne
Kuch kamre usme sone ne
Ek kamra hai mehmaan ka
Ek kamra rakhya hai rone ne
Re taabad-tod pade aansu
Tezaab ki tariya farsh jalaya
Koi maali bhi nahi milna re
Jab husn ka yo gulaab jalaya
Meri bebasi ka aalam yo
Ke poochhe bata nahi sakda main
Mere phone mein tera number hai
Par chaaha ke nahi mila sakda main

[Interlude: Xvir Grewal]
Ye ishq bedard bada

[Verse 5: Dhanda Nyoliwala]
Ishq hai nahi kade manne nyu to bata
Dulhan ke darpan mein, choodi ki khan-khan mein
Meera ke paanya mein, ghungroo ki chan-chan mein
Dariya mein, naawan mein, shehar mein, gaawan mein
Mahki fizawan mein, sard hawaawan mein
Tapti hui dhoop mein, chhaayi ghataawan mein
Aashiq ki yaad mein, phaili hui baayaan mein
Raanjhe ki wanjhli mein, Heer ki choodi mein
Sohni ke ghade mein, Mahiwal ki doori mein
Toote hue teer mein, patke maas mein
Sahiba Mirze ne aakhri saans mein
Ke kahya hoga?

[Chorus: Dhanda Nyoliwala]
Logo re ishq na kariyo
Be aayi maut na mariyo
Sutya ke teer tootenge
Mirze jyu pyaar na kariyo

[Refrain: Xvir Grewal]
Pyaar na kariyo na kariyo

[Outro: Dhanda Nyoliwala]
Ishq bhi yaara karke dekh liya
Jinde-ji bhi marke dekh liya
Ghutt sabr ka bhar ke dekh liya
Ib hadiyan mein khoon nahi hai
Sab kuch paa liya zindagi mein
Par zindagi mein sukoon nahi hai
